is a male bearing the labels: “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935E8E03F1F4FDFEFBA3FD4D" authority="Godet" authorityName="Godet" box="[969,1138,620,646]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="491" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="saxicola">
