<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935E8E03F13CFD02FC4BFD61" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[769,922,656,682]" pageId="7" pageNumber="491" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
