</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E935E8E03F2FAFD26FD03FCF1" pageId="7" pageNumber="491" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935E8E03F2FAFD26FA4DFCDD" blockId="7.[151,1437,620,826]" pageId="7" pageNumber="491">
There was no statement about the authorship of the red label marked “TYPE”; it was perhaps left by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935E8E03F777FD26FF0AFD39" author="Mlynar, Z." pageId="7" pageNumber="491" pagination="73 - 111" refId="ref11903" refString="Mlynar, Z. (1979) Beitrag zur Kenntnis der Osteuropaischen und Sibirischen Harpalus-Arten (Col., Carabidae). Koleopterologische Rundschau, 54, 73 - 111." type="journal article" year="1979">Mlynař (1979</bibRefCitation>
, p. 73), who was able to study a number of types of Dejean’s collection. I hereby recognize this specimen as the 
<typeStatus id="54C98807935E8E03F2FDFD6EFEF3FCDD" box="[192,290,764,790]" pageId="7" pageNumber="491">holotype</typeStatus>
by monotypy, according to the original description. A key to this species is available in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935E8E03F6C0FD6EFA46FCDD" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[1277,1431,764,790]" pageId="7" pageNumber="491" refId="ref12634" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2011) Genus Tschitscherinellus. Arndt, E., Schnitter, P., Sfenthourakis, S. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (Eds.), Ground beetles (Carabidae) of Greece. Pensoft, Sofia, pp. 163." type="book" year="2011">Wrase (2011)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935E8E03F2FAFCB2FD03FCF1" blockId="7.[151,1437,620,826]" box="[199,722,800,826]" pageId="7" pageNumber="491">It is distributed in East Europe and the Levant.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
